<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="constitution-n">constitution <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌkɒnstɪ'tjuːʃn/    美 /ˌkɑːnstə'tuːʃn/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>宪法；章程：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>According to the American Constitution, presidential elections are held every four years. 
依据美国宪法，总统大选每4年举行一次。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>体质；体格：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A hard life and <strong>a weak constitution</strong> shortened Robert Burn’s life. 
艰辛的生活和虚弱的体质缩短了罗伯特·彭斯的寿命。</p><footer>译林⑧ – 1</footer></div></div>